<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6527] Make custom filters plugin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6527</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;More and more custom Filters are created.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should provide plugin mechanism for these custom Filters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12602116">HBASE-6527</key>
            <summary>Make custom filters plugin</summary>
